{"type": "article", "id": 1071, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-06-09T17:03:10Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 6, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604215023QMK2jUyGFbCv7aJB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t1.  Distortion by <span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.baobaoisseymiyake.com/en/park_04_distortion.html#\" target=\"_blank\">BAO BAO ISSEY MIYAKE</a> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t三宅一生的 BAO BAO PARK 系列最新作品，Distortion（变形），黄色、黑色、白色三款颜色。这款超有立体感的手拿包完全由一个平面的不规则多边形和三组搭扣组成，设计感与科技感十足。 6 月 12 日即将在日本的东京、大阪店首发。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215016q21st93JMo0ezKiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215016u7xVkD30OrLfdano.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t2.  <span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://www.jyrobike.com/\">Jyrobike</a> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">“永远不要试图重新发明轮子？”英国公司 Jyrobike 并不相信这句话，<span></span><span>他们的</span><span>目标对准 3-8 岁的儿童，让孩子在一个下午就轻松学会骑自行车</span>。<span>Jyrobike</span>自动平衡自行车<span>运用了回转仪技术，<span>无需任何辅助的小轮子或者支架就可以保持不倒，</span>这项技术也运用于保持直升机的稳定。目前他们还在 kickstarter 上筹钱，</span><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/529668138/jyrobike-auto-balance-bicycle\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>支持他们。<br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215017M5zOTy8uS3J1r97V.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215018D5Gu1U7yOgH6iJZN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215018aostlW47NOdGgTx6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215019i7mGlHRajqzt6k4o.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134809GOsFJ7gIZStCTE3Y.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">3.  B<span>utterfly Stool </span>by 柳宗理</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><span>MoMA</span><span>美术馆和卢浮宫的永久藏品。</span><span></span>椅子看起来很像蝴蝶展翅的样子，从正面看起来是汉字天，又像日本神社的鸟居。在做工方面，曲线柔美，考验木工成形技术，椅子由2根螺丝1根金属棒组成了简约的造型。<a href=\"http://www.sempre.jp/item/463605/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>你也可以拥有。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215020NX6FyRUcjPLmsVHD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134809EKjmIFRaYbkyVMxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t4.  Babylon series by <span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://samuelwilkinson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Samuel Wilkinson</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t多面体文具系列，包含笔、笔筒、剪刀、订书器、胶带和一只闹钟。满足基本办公需求的同时，也能<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">为你的办公桌提气不少。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215021V1YWACGpkNTuL8PR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215021DR6Zfo3y92wq7kE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t5.  Le Nid (The Nest) by <a href=\"http://www.jeanjullien.com\" target=\"_blank\">Jean Jullien</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t“鸟瞰”城市全貌？<span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_25__\"></span>法国设计师 Jean Jullien 在法国城市南斯市中心 144 米高的建筑顶层搭设了自己的艺术作品 The Nest、同时它还是一个观景台、一间酒吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134810C8ujA7Y54KN3pXkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215022pDue1vqi36fJHASw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215022I1ainjpvRdoZ5NOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}